column2: SELECT TOP # Q.BestObjID, u, g, Q.ra, Q.dec, Q.z, G.ObjID, G.ra, G.dec, P.z, G.u, G.g, G.r, G.i, G.z, N.distance into mydb.test from Galaxy   as G, 		   QSO       as Q, 		   Neighbors       as N,		   SpecObj         as S,   Photoz          as P 		 WHERE Q.BestObjID = S.BestObjID 		   and Q.z > #   and Q.z < #   and u < #   and g <#   and G.g>#   and G.ObjID = P.ObjID   and P.z BETWEEN # and #   and photoErrorClass=#   and Q.z>P.z   and Q.class  in (&&&, &&&) 	   and G.ObjID = N.ObjID		   and Q.BestObjID = N.NeighborObjID  	   and N.distance < #/#
